rows.label: qev051503_MSG0001
rows.name:
Ha ha! Now Lularita, strongest Nopon in Drongo
Caravan, enters fray! ...No, wait. Scratch that.
Strongest Nopon ANYWHERE![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev051503_MSG0002
rows.name:
Lularita came here today to prove she is toughest one
on entire planet![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev051503_MSG0003
rows.name:
...Hmm? Friend wants to know if Lularita is going to
fight [ST:gender p1=him p2=her ] in bloody combat to death?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev051503_MSG0004
rows.name:
Oh ho ho hooooo! Friend is so amusing!
...But no. That is ridiculous. What if Lularita got hurt?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev051503_MSG0005
rows.name:
No, friend will face the army of raging nopopotamuses
Lularita spent ton of time and money training.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev051503_MSG0006
rows.name:
Now brace for battle while Lularita braces for
spectating from safe distance![ST:wait ]
